data.description: Executive Pool Home on the lake in Stoney Brook at Gateway. Assumable 1st Mortgage at 2.75% Agents see confidential remarks! 2900+ sqft 5 bedroom 3 1/2 baths 24 X 24 Tile throughout 1 bdrm downstairs, tile in main areas, carpet with premium padding in all bedrooms and upstairs area, ceiling fans throughout the house. Kitchen features level 2 Marble counter tops and backsplash from Brazil, soft close cabinets. Stainless steel appliances. Motivated Seller! Hurricane Rated windows and doors. 2021 Ducane 2 stage 5 ton A/C Unit with ecobee smart thermostat. Huge Screened in Pool area featuring a heated salt water pool and spa. Heater replaced in 2021 with app for temp and pool and spa lights. Lights and misters add to the ambiance by the pool as you relax having morning coffee while looking over the lake or enjoy stunning sunsets! Stoneybrook features lots of amenities and with low HOA fees. 24-hour Guard Gate along with Security Patrol, fitness center, heated pool, spa, kiddie pool, toddler playground, basketball courts, tennis courts, hockey rink, soccer and baseball fields. The community keeps the calendar packed with free community events, food trucks, holiday parties, and parades.
